{"tid":1234920,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"未來大方向 同意請正評幫推 不足請更正","createTime":"2019-06-17T04:32:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-17T14:02:44.000Z","uid":82547,"like":37,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"ae7d904780cb27593702baaf75dd9d67eb5dee03","tid":1234920,"uid":82547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T04:32:20.000Z","msg":"依家最重要一定係<span style=\"color: red;\">平反612係非暴動同正視警權過大</span>，和理非同勇武各有用處，可互補不足，應合作，不應分化。和理非可吸引民眾，<span style=\"color: red;\">依家政府諗住打民意牌，所以和理非係民意上可制衡政府。</span>衝係要，但唔係每次都衝，等開會或合適時先再衝，<span style=\"color: red;\">一定要有衝既理由同目的，唔好亂衝，唔係會失民意同白白送頭。</span><br />\n1. <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">設deadline</span></span><br />\n6月尾就g20,外交壓力一定有，所以政府諗住用和平同拖，等市民心灰同件事淡。<span style=\"color: red;\">設死線可阻止政府拖落去，同埋政府唔理，就有合理理由去衝，話政府忽視民意，出師有名。</span><br />\n<br />\n2. <span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">文宣</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">長輩圖，外國報導，本地宣傳。</span>多管齊下，香港人好善忘，唔可以比人淡忘，所以宣傳一定要做足。遊行都可以吸引外國報導，絕對有用。每星期遊行係ok,但唔可以拖太耐，否則就變左日常活動，吸引唔到人注意，無左作用。<br />\n<br />\n3.<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">計劃</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">短期</span>而言，逼政府平反612，正視警權過大。基本上一定會有衝突，所以<span style=\"color: red;\">裝一定要準備好，諗方法改善聯絡同戰術</span>，eg現場人士可自行開gp傾，以防有鬼。同埋要<span style=\"color: red;\">速戰速決，g20過後香港影響力應該會細左</span>，所以死線一定要有。另外，正視警權可確保以後既遊行等活動既安全同防止打壓，一定要做。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">中期</span>而言，立法會選舉要鸁，先有機會搶返主導權，所以<span style=\"color: red;\">登記選民，幫住老人院既長者改地址取消選民資格或帶佢地去投票。</span>同埋有位巴打搞左個黨分 薄民建聯啲票，可以幫下手，減低佢地當選機會。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">長期</span>而言，如果今次成功，可以<span style=\"color: red;\">食住個勢，要求真普選</span>。咁有立法會有民選特首先會有自主權，同埋大家可以入政府做，多啲自己人，有咩事都容易進行，慢慢換血換走班親中。<br />\n<br />\n第一次出post,有咩不足請指教及包容。<br />\n內容都係大方向，詳細點做要靠各位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c89418e58f32f8bf07927aa7bd900592919baa7e","tid":1234920,"uid":82547,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T04:35:50.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"aa830e23b8f987cf8b0e7bb879fe008661e33764","tid":1234920,"uid":82547,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T04:37:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"968e3a356b2ce4ad9be85f2469a959e673ba1193","tid":1234920,"uid":82547,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T04:39:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"923c00fdad112b223ffdf5dbbf483fd11ebaec45","tid":1234920,"uid":82547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T04:40:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9a7f46a800646601acf791b61728b3e0dd901a4c","tid":1234920,"uid":82547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T04:42:25.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"db22a9730111229233d49aed968b367caa5a24ba","tid":1234920,"uid":82547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T04:44:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"dac163f50eb06e84601432cc113f8648f6b0d606","tid":1234920,"uid":82547,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T04:48:55.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"227d6e44e568fc5a650f2e28b75a23398f101949","tid":1234920,"uid":82547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T04:54:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bbc8d903c2a75bcb80b1641f69a32647e72192ba","tid":1234920,"uid":82547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T04:58:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"77109e3df10f58ef1db806b3d60b3fb5a127dd6a","tid":1234920,"uid":82547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T05:49:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3d854248b2985cc3104aa08be6678739be8ef1e2","tid":1234920,"uid":82547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T05:59:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0c4c81e4661e403e18f3fccb9af197a1a44f65b6","tid":1234920,"uid":82547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T06:05:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5b5301227f